The paper discusses the security issue in wireless networks, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of non-orthogonal multiple access (NOMA) and channel estimation techniques also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to the multimedia (cs.MM) and systems and control (cs.SY) categories. Additionally, the paper proposes to optimize the transmit powers, which is a common approach in cryptography and security (cs.CR).
